<view class="container">
    <view class="swiper">
        <swiper indicator-dots="{{indicatorDots}}" autoplay="{{autoplay}}" interval="{{interval}}" duration="{{duration}}" bindchange="changeSwiper">
            <block wx:for="{{imgUrls}}">
                <swiper-item>
                    <image src="{{item}}" class="slide-image" width="355" height="150"/>
                </swiper-item>
            </block>
        </swiper>
        <!--view class="swiper-dots">
            <block wx:for="{{imgUrls}}">
                <block wx:if="{{current == index}}">
                    <view class="current"></view>
                </block>
                <block wx:else>
                    <view></view>
                </block>
            </block>
        </view-->
    </view>

    <view class="basic-info">
        <text class="title">{{id}}新西兰Meliata麦克鲁蜂蜜UMF5+340g</text>
        <text class="price">¥149.50</text>
        <text>原产国市场售价 31.99 NZD(新西兰元)</text>
        <text>按当前汇率折合人民币 ＝ ¥156.03</text>
        <text>中国网上零售价价：¥189</text>
        <text>中国线下实体价价：¥258</text>
        <view class="location">
            <image src="/image/flags/en.png" class="icon-flag"></image><text>新西兰</text>
        </view>
    </view>

    <view class="sku-info">
        <view>颜色<text>“黑色”</text></view>
        <view>数量</view>
    </view>

    <view class="smiple-intro">
        <text>1. 产自新西兰纯天然无污染蜂蜜产区，无添加麦卢卡蜂蜜； 2. UMF 5+具有一定消炎功能，对肠胃有调节作用； 3. 精确到每瓶蜂蜜的质量追踪系统，安全有保障。</text>
        <text>每天每天15:00从上海自贸区发货</text><text>七天无理由退货</text>
    </view>

    <view class="floatCart">
        <view class="viewCart">
            <navigator url="/pages/cart/cart" open-type="switchTab">查看购物车</navigator>
        </view>
        <view class="addToCart">
            <button>加入购物车</button>
        </view>
    </view>
